title: 200 Pcs 15 mm Stainless Steel Pipe Screen Filters,Smoking Pipe Filters Screens with Storage Box,Gauze Ash Catcher Smoking Screen
features: 【Package Includes】You will receive 200 pieces of 15mm stainless steel pipe screens, providing ample quantity for long-term use, replacement, and sharing. A practical addition to any toolkit or smoking accessory collection.

【Premium Material】Made from high-quality 304 stainless steel, these mesh screens are rust-resistant, corrosion-resistant, odorless, spark-free, and built for durability. They are easy to clean and can be reused multiple times without losing their shape.

【Effective Mesh Design】The fine mesh structure allows for smooth airflow and even smoke distribution while effectively blocking debris, hot ash, and residue from entering the pipe—making your sessions cleaner and more enjoyable.

【Functional & Easy to Use】These pipe filters help prevent clogging and reduce the risk of inhaling harmful ash. Simply place into your pipe or device to improve filtration and simplify post-use cleaning.

【Wide Application】Suitable for use with most smoking accessories and can also be used in plumbing, air conditioners, washing machines, vacuums, evaporators, and more. A versatile tool for both smoking needs and household equipment maintenance.
description: Keep your smoking sessions clean and efficient with this 200 Pcs 15 mm Stainless Steel Pipe Screen Set. Made from high-quality 304 stainless steel, these durable and reusable mesh filters provide smooth airflow, effective debris blocking, and enhanced user experience. A must-have for any smoker or DIY enthusiast. Benefits of Using 200 Pcs 15 mm Stainless Steel Pipe Screens Cleaner, Smoother Experience: The fine mesh design allows for optimal airflow while effectively trapping ash and debris—ensuring a smoother, cleaner smoke with every use. Durable and Reusable: Crafted from rust-resistant 304 stainless steel, these pipe screens are built to last. They can be cleaned and reused multiple times, offering a cost-effective, eco-friendly alternative to disposable options. Multi-Purpose Use: Beyond smoking, these screens are ideal for plumbing systems, air conditioning units, vacuums, and other household equipment—making them a versatile addition to your toolbox. How to Use and Care Instructions How to Use: Select a 15 mm screen and gently shape it to fit the bowl or cavity of your pipe or device. Insert the screen into the desired area, ensuring it lays flat and covers the hole completely. Use as normal—enjoy better airflow and filtration. Care Instructions: After use, remove the screen and rinse under warm water. For deeper cleaning, soak in rubbing alcohol and rinse thoroughly. Let dry completely before reuse. Store in a dry container to prevent moisture-related damage.
